        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Introducing Alp. Cherbonier.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Nackitosh </placeName><date when="1824-07-07">July 7th 1824</date>.</p>
<p>Dr Sir.</p>

<p>I take pleasure with this to introduce to you <hi rend="italic"><persName>Mr. Cherbonier</persName></hi> with
whom I have been long Acquainted, he is a gentleman who posseses
the Esteem of all his Acquaintances, as a scholar, a man of Integrity
and honour, and in every respect worthy of your notice.</p>

<p><persName>John Sibley</persName>    [Rubric]</p>
<p>[Addressed:]   <persName>Honble Stephen F. Austin Esquire</persName>  <persName>Brazos   </persName><persName>Mr
Cherbonier</persName>.</p>

        </div1>
    </body>
